poles go toward each other

00:30:57.610 --> 00:31:00.010
and then they split,
and they become complex.

00:31:00.010 --> 00:31:02.545
Complex is good.

00:31:02.545 --> 00:31:05.450
But this still has the
problem that the mass spring

00:31:05.450 --> 00:31:08.640
