00:40:29.480 --> 00:40:31.400
If the weight starts
to move this way

00:40:31.400 --> 00:40:34.040
what should the hunky motor do?

00:40:34.040 --> 00:40:37.440
Push the cart that way.

00:40:37.440 --> 00:40:38.700
So that's the idea.

00:40:38.700 --> 00:40:44.030
So I've got a one
dimensional inverted pendulum

00:40:44.030 --> 00:40:48.290
