fact that the car is moving

00:41:54.450 --> 00:41:57.930
is to compute torques about
the point of insertion.

00:41:57.930 --> 00:42:01.110
Then I can represent the
effect of the moving car

00:42:01.110 --> 00:42:05.620
as a pseudo force on the mass.

00:42:05.620 --> 00:42:07.120
That pseudo force
is in proportion

00:42:07.120 --> 00:42:11.000
